" Notes:
"   A whole lot of thigs here are based or just shamesly copied
"   from Amir Salihefendic's basic .vimrc, which can be found here:
"   https://github.com/amix/vimrc
"
" Sections:
"    -> Vundle
"    -> Plugins
"    -> General
